name: Seba
description: SEBA token is one of the leading tokens currently in the Crypto market that is directly connected to animations and video marketing. SEBA token platforms offer a plethora of unique features and opportunities to its investor;purchasing animations is amongst them. Investors looking for animated videos or animations, in general, can purchase animations for their business. SEBA token also makes it easier for animators to purchase or sell animations on the market through SEBA NFT.
